Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:26.14,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始终寻找心的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:32.52,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}待掌中接获那份沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:38.06,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}又备下宽敞的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:51.08,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将坚定的心就此珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:13.64,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}未来带有怎样的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:19.61,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}还是保持未知为好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:25.19,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在难以入眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:36.62,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}封印在抽屉的最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:42.71,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}光明 阴影 泪水 声响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:51.89,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}都令我怦然心动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:57.06,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始终探寻注定的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:03.32,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}难得抓住一线希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:13.95,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}下一个注定又在远方招手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:22.92,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如此终而复始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:43.23,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}尚未扎稳根基之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:48.78,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}岂可掐去希望之花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.74,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}总有些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:55.87,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}分毫也无法动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:03.75,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}而那正是心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:08.76,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始终寻找心的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:14.85,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}待掌中接获那份沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:20.52,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}又备下宽敞的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:34.62,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将坚定的心就此珍藏
