Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:36.15,next_title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad2\fad(300,0)\pos(1112,600)}「毕业」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙上校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜破坏RA221基地作战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能还以乌鲁伽鲁一点颜色了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 今后的作战也有点希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的战斗现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直小看我们的乌鲁伽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本次战斗之后 肯定会有大动作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要准备应对乌鲁伽鲁的反击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也已经确认敌人有所行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天音副官 这里轮不到你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样一来 MJP的驾驶员培养也上轨道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能培养出许多像他们一样优秀的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利也就有望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要推进增产ASHMB
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 那战斗真的很艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责整备的可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的Rhinos是你们的ASHMB的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你们也能打得那么漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该能打得更漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要更好地掌握自己的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的机体里是植入了DNA的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你驾驶它 操作就会是相对简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不要只依赖机械的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单方面的依赖关系是不会持久的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 找我什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想要新的色情影片 我手头可没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们接到了再度返回学园的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以来跟你说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 肯定又会在别的地方碰面的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 敌人似乎也已经开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上次战斗的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,储存在Rhinos里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也承担为下一代取得战斗数据的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之后会回到最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,储存在Rhinos里的数据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是前辈还是我们 都是类似数据一样的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doberman接下来会去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是回到最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你们怎么在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我们也不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子 关键的地方少根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是遗憾五人组
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的攻击能成功 也是多亏了前辈们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你们可别在战斗中把我们的名声都败光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感觉很宽慰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宽慰个啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这么努力 结果受到这种对待？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃风教官叫你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾小队的前辈们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾…小队？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那是故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是真的误会了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业…指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 你们将结束培养期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式配属到GDF军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说只有你们几个跳级毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也将调离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去担任戈迪利昂的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 去整理你们宿舍内的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天回到玫瑰之星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备接受下一个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白没
Comment: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#插曲#
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就让我们毕业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「今后会毫无顾忌地把你们丢上战场！」的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点落寞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚来这里的时候 我都没想过以后会有这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为当时感觉就是被人不管三七二十一扔进这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你们分到同一个小队的时候 感觉可震惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下一个小队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木俊一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骏河中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日立出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钉宫惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入江环
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都比我小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不懂的 尽管问我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来 骏河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始你基本不怎么说话的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我都不知道该说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的记忆都被消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了上课和天气之外也没什么可说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这上课啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbits小队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的攻击力和机动力都很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是协调性 集中力和动作稳定性都是E
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是协调性 是E-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是说她的罩杯 那是差不多这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆是F就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,评分最差就是E了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么 从那之后就能开口聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我能拿走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是之前住在这间宿舍的学生的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那么残破了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我看的第一部漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这下爽快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不用再回来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们率先驾驶最新锐的ASHMB并且毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任谁都不会想到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做梦都想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想一个人躲起来哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想最后再画张素描
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\pos(566,298)\fs72\frz44.633\c&H7EADC8&}遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来 完全摆脱不了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒要问你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来整理书桌里的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(499,184)\frz13.64}交到绝佳{\c&H6772EC&}女友{\c&HFFFFFF&}的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是给男生看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\frz10.11\pos(453,227)\c&H2A1A0B&\3c&H82A5EF&}跃动的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…上课时候都在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格说别人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪我们被人说是遗憾五人组
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木说想最后绕校园一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的ASHMB现在正运来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天音大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白户中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚开完会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的经济组织都吵着要ASHMB的技术和机体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们之前一直被对手摁着打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是头一次取得胜利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASHMB和MJP机关引起注目也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们对ASHMB如此眼红 并不是为了和敌人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是想自己国家爬到顶端而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和敌人战斗很不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过地球上的政治手腕也叫人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看他们对技术的渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的想资助格兰赛列都市学园
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有的想让驾驶员入学就读
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些不归你管的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为西蒙司令目前不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去学园了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 已经收拾好了行李
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天应该就能出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 让他们正式成为军队一员还有点早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还不能完全熟练地驾驶ASHMB
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对茱莉亚系统也有点困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入江环和骏河中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于天生性格的缘故 比较适应系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 麻木和钉宫这两人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了前线就会发怵 不能发挥实力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日立出虽然时不时能展现出爆发性的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不够稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们在这里已经学不到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵茱莉亚系统的方法 也只有在实战中才能学到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在生死悬于一线的情况下才能学到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做明天的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASHMB？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 实物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟练习机体完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们非得进行模拟演习？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得很早嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个模拟演习而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要这么紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为是模拟演习才紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能比战斗还吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的要做这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我昨天说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue1和Red5表演对接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gold4在标准重力下射击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为使用的是实体弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要注意测算重力 风向 湿度和大气密度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Purple2负责指挥 Rose3从上空进行支援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演习就是这个形式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演我不擅长的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为之前你在全宇宙面前失败了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就好了 有个表现机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就开开炮啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个地方指挥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是表演用高台嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概这是最丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 Rabbits小队将进行模拟演习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到毕业前还有这种任务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是摆脱遗憾五人组这个称号的好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 是不是想一口气成为学园的英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个很棒的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得我们别失败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue1 Gold4 Red5 升空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue1 Red5 对接
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rose3 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环 你飞得比计划中要低啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gold4 就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没人看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们给谁鼓掌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演习到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前很多地方对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不在了 会挺寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们很快也会上前线的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦 以后再会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾五人组
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业生 入场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颁发军阶章
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入江环
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钉宫惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木俊一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都在干什么啊 麻木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一辈子的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概你胃里穿了三个洞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的风头都被你抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言那才不叫风头！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点上来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会再回这儿了来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点…落寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后大家在哪里 那里就是我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们五个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以遗憾小队的身份努力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小队名字搞错了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫「是吗」！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜笨蛋蠢才呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:55.87,next_title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad2\pos(1030,600)}「欲望的大本营」
